<chapter id=UsingFrontPanel>Front Panel Tasks


The instructions assume that you are using a mouse.
Most tasks can also be done without a mouse; see 
<link hyperlink="Intromgr DesktopKeyboardNav" Jump> Keyboard Shortcuts
for the Desktop<\link> for more information.

