<s1 id=ToChangeNumberOfWorkspaces>To Add and Remove Workspaces
	<idx>workspace:adding<\idx>
	<idx>workspace:deleting<\idx>

<procedure>To Add a Workspace

<list order>
<item>Point to a workspace switch area.
<item>Choose Add Workspace from the <link FPPopupMenus>workspace button's pop-up menu<\link>.
<\list>

A workspace named "New" is added (see <xref TorenameWorkspace>).

<procedure>To Remove a Workspace
<list order>

<item> Point to the workspace switch button.

<item> Choose Delete Workspace from the
  <link FPPopupMenus>workspace button's pop-up menu<\link>.
<\list>

<procedure>See Also
<list bullet tight>
<item> <xref TorenameWorkspace>
<\list>

